definition: to break into/to force one's way into/to barge into
to crowd in/to cram in/to force others aside/to press/to squeeze/to find (time in one's busy schedule)
to go forward/to advance/to go in/to enter/to put in/to submit/to take in/to admit/(math.) base of a number system/classifier for sections in a building or residential compound

sentences.english: It is very difficult to become part of Mandalay's supply chain.
sentences.chinese: 想要挤进M公司供应链的窄门，是非常困难的一件事。

sentences.english: Two girlfriends and I piled into a car and headed to Aspen, Colo.
sentences.chinese: 我和两个女友挤进一辆车，驰向科罗拉多的阿斯彭。

sentences.english: For he had healed many; insomuch that they pressed upon him for to touch him, as many as had plagues.
sentences.chinese: 他治好了许多人，所以凡有灾病的，都挤进来要摸他。

sentences.english: Seeing the hall was crowded, he elbowed himself in.
sentences.chinese: 看到大厅里都是人，他挤进去了。

sentences.english: He interposed himself between them to stop them fighting .
sentences.chinese: 他挤进两人中间，阻止他们打架。

sentences.english: As more blood is forced in, the tiny cavern swells .
sentences.chinese: 当更多的血挤进来时，微小的蓄水池就胀大。

sentences.english: He bribed himself onto the committee.
sentences.chinese: 他暗通关节，钻营投机挤进了委员会。

sentences.english: She can even squeeze herself into boxes just 50cms squared.
sentences.chinese: 她甚至可以让自己挤进仅仅50厘米见方的盒子里。

sentences.english: They all crowded into their small living room.
sentences.chinese: 他们都挤进了他们的小客厅。

sentences.english: Finally she was forced into a pocket formed by broken concret chunks.
sentences.chinese: 最后她被挤进一个破碎的水泥块形成的口袋状的地方。

sentences.english: The panic - stricken passengers tried to rush the life - boats .
sentences.chinese: 惊慌的旅客争先恐后，想挤进救生艇。

sentences.english: So many people crammed into the bus that it was impossible to close the door.
sentences.chinese: 在高峰时间这么多的人挤进公共汽车，连门也关不上。

sentences.english: The door has cracked open. We are all going to try to collectively crash through it.
sentences.chinese: 门已经打开了一条缝，我们将努力一起挤进去。

sentences.english: Crowds packed into the cinemas on a wet day.
sentences.chinese: 在雨天，一大群人挤进电影院。

sentences.english: Two women tried to push their way through.
